# Build context exclusions for `docker build` / GoReleaser docker context.
# Keep the context small — irrelevant for COPY-only Dockerfile but useful
# defense if the build ever switches to multi-stage Go-inside builds.

.git/
.github/
.task/
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/

# Editor / OS noise
*.swp
.DS_Store
*.bak

# Local build artifacts
sopds
sopds-tts
zipdupes
sopds-tts-rs/target/
zipdupes-rs/target/
dist/

# Local config / DB dumps (in case they reappear)
config.yaml
sopds_backup.dump*
*.lst
tags
test_baseline.txt

# Documentation that ships in the GitHub Release archives but doesn't
# need to live inside the runtime image.
PROGRESS.md
NOTICE.md
LICENSE
README.md

# Subprojects with their own ecosystems
sopds-tts-rs/
zipdupes-rs/
fb2converters/
fetch/

# Tests
*_test.go
